metadata.name: Widow's Curse
metadata.description:
In a small town near Okinawa, a defiant group of teens went on a pranking spree. When one prank goes too far, the teens accidently burned down an old cob webbed covered house, with the town's oldest resident in it, a widowed mysterious spider collector.

Fearing they committed murder, the teens are on the run from the law. Little did they know, the law wasn't the only ones hunting them...
